osmtags 0.1.0
  • Reference

    Free search

    search_key_value.Rd

    Search for tags, keys or relation roles.

    search_key_value(query, ...)

search_keyword(query, ...)

search_role(query, ...)

search_value(query, ...)

    Source

    https://taginfo.openstreetmap.org/taginfo/apidoc

    Arguments

    query

    Substring to search for. Used to search key/value combinations in case of search_key_value, keywords in wiki pages in case of search_keyword, relation roles in case of search_role, and values in case of search_value

    Value

    For search_key_value and search_keyword returns a dataframe containing the matched key-value combinations. For search_role returns a dataframe containing the matched relation type and role.

    Examples
